Introduction

MYTEEN (Korean: 마이틴; Japanese: マイティン) is a South Korean boy group that consists of 7 members under The Music Works. The group includes Taevin, Chunjin, Eunsu, Xiheon, Junseop, Yuvin, and Hanseul.

After promoting for 2 years, the group officially disbanded on August 21, 2019.
